Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.86,0:03:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是因为这辆车很稀奇吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.86,0:03:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是因为这样我才讨厌日本的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.56,0:03:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,单纯、轻浮、又没知性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.43,0:03:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好怀念在英国的时候啊
