Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.49,0:04:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是肮脏
