Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.62,0:06:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.52,0:06:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷居然会在这个大学里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.29,0:06:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们两个果然被命运的红丝线牵系着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.96,0:06:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繭实在是太感激了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.43,0:06:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.20,0:06:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.73,0:06:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀？你还在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.50,0:06:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这么突然对阿薰做了什么事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.27,0:06:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事？啊？接吻的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这只是理所当然的打招呼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也会做不是吗？你是美国人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.21,0:07:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…跟阿薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.76,0:07:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了吗？你的脸好红
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.54,0:07:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你到底跟花菱少爷是什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.07,0:07:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我是…阿薰的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.71,0:07:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道你就是美幸繭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.79,0:07:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 没错 我就是繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.86,0:07:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 你长大了呢 我完全都认不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.16,0:07:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的呢 几年没见面了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四年了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊 四年了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.71,0:07:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么说来小繭你已经16岁了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.47,0:08:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看起来变成熟了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.64,0:08:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的吗？这一定是在英国念书的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在英国…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.78,0:08:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才那样子打招呼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.32,0:08:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷也稍微变了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.65,0:08:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变得越来越帅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.86,0:08:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈哈 哪有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.06,0:08:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像没有我们可以插嘴的余地了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.80,0:08:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 学姐 你刚刚是想要说什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.47,0:08:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于花菱学长的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.57,0:08:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么都没有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.97,0:08:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰你来一下 过来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.08,0:08:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你认识那个女孩？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 有点熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.02,0:08:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道是她对你说了什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.32,0:08:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 请你原谅她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.15,0:08:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然她很好强 但是其实她是个好女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.19,0:08:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样子完全看不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.16,0:08:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.39,0:08:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.23,0:08:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又说了让人生气的话了呢 这样不行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.23,0:08:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来 好好的道歉一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.04,0:09:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.84,0:09:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说的太过分了 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.78,0:09:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实追根究底 原来就是我撞到你不对啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.25,0:09:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你 蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.12,0:09:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原谅你了 真是太好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 花菱少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是个天真的女孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对吧 蒂娜学姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.49,0:09:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.53,0:09:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.50,0:09:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇啊 这些就是花菱少爷拍的照片啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.97,0:09:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太漂亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.74,0:09:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太漂亮了…什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.51,0:09:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明就是因为作品不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.25,0:09:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天才花了一小时左右拍出来的东西而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.68,0:09:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且还是一张五块钱的特价品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.22,0:09:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 也看一下其他人的作品嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.12,0:09:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有比这些更不错的照片喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.33,0:09:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他的就不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.66,0:10:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起这个 花菱少爷能带我看一下校园吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.57,0:10:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是没有问题啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.10,0:10:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是小繭你今天为什么会来这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.64,0:10:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来事先参观的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.31,0:10:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事先？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.44,0:10:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要进这所学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.18,0:10:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进这所学校啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.78,0:10:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？进这所学校？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.75,0:10:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.56,0:10:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是跳级啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.10,0:10:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在英国留学读中学时就跳级两年毕业了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.30,0:10:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在成为了日本的归国子女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.84,0:10:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？真是厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.57,0:10:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了能早点回到日本 我相当的努力念书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.51,0:10:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 小繭你是不喜欢英国吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.18,0:10:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我很喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.99,0:10:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那里环境很诗意 时间也过的很悠闲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.62,0:11:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你为什么会想早点回到日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.23,0:11:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.30,0:11:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有英国没有 而日本才有的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.64,0:11:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,英国没有 而日本才有的东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.77,0:11:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.14,0:11:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,校内大致上就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.51,0:11:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.25,0:11:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托你的福 我已经了解校内的情况了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.68,0:11:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 不用客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.65,0:11:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 你什么时候会来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.82,0:11:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从下个礼拜开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.72,0:11:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那如果来的话 记得来摄影社玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.63,0:11:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.63,0:11:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个 花菱少爷接下来有事情要忙吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.27,0:11:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 是没什么事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.44,0:11:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可以的话要不要来我家呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.54,0:11:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来我家吃晚餐吧 我有好多话想跟你聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.91,0:12:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊 虽说是没事 但不待在摄影展也不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.25,0:12:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.96,0:12:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果还要去吃晚餐就有点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.06,0:12:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 好 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.37,0:12:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你晚餐要在外面吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.07,0:12:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 我碰到了以前的朋友 也先告诉蒂娜跟妙子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.88,0:12:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有 我可能会稍微晚一点才回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.95,0:12:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.39,0:12:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道早退的代价吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.02,0:12:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最后一天的整理你可是要一个人做喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.43,0:12:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.80,0:12:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才是事情非常谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.04,0:12:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.28,0:13:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 我是繭大小姐的随从 我叫西圆寺琉伽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.81,0:13:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.88,0:13:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车子在那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来我真是吓了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.86,0:13:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大小姐她除了双亲之外还有可以敞开心胸的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.96,0:13:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊 虽然她长的那么大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.60,0:13:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟那时比起来还是没变啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.54,0:13:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大小姐她常常都很寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.27,0:13:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷 请你让大小姐她能多开心一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.51,0:13:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.68,0:13:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 我会尽我所能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.35,0:13:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.53,0:13:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是太过分了 爸爸妈妈都是一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.86,0:13:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去国外的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.46,0:13:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,常常去参加各种社交场合 还有接待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.17,0:13:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就说英文是必要的 而自己决定叫我去留学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.10,0:14:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毕业之后又擅自决定我要进的大学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.97,0:14:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们两个都完全没考虑到我的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.14,0:14:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很过分对吧 花菱少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.61,0:14:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸妈都是为了你才这么做的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.25,0:14:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经不是小孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.79,0:14:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己的事情我能够自己解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.12,0:14:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸妈还是老样子很忙吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夫妇两个都是工作狂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.70,0:14:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美幸纺织是世界最有名的纺织工业呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.40,0:14:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这也是没办法的 你爸爸现在在哪儿？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.87,0:14:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在法国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.37,0:14:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你妈妈呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.88,0:14:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈在芬兰 为王室设计王妃的新礼服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么时候才会回来呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.82,0:14:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁知道 反正回来又只会啰嗦 还不如不回来好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.31,0:15:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.84,0:15:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有好久没来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.61,0:15:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好大的房子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.85,0:15:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里比得上花菱家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.02,0:15:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来这里 快点啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了吗？葵大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.83,0:15:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天晚上薰不在 我在发什么呆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.30,0:15:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总觉得…只有两个人好空啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.77,0:15:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 花菱少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.34,0:15:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以坐在花菱少爷你身边吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.55,0:15:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.82,0:15:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.50,0:16:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小繭你吃的真顺手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.96,0:16:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你用不惯刀叉吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.37,0:16:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不是不习惯 因为我平常都是用筷子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.81,0:16:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我倒是不太会用筷子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.68,0:16:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.31,0:16:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.62,0:16:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请给花菱少爷一双筷子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.22,0:16:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.19,0:16:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上就会送来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.82,0:16:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.16,0:16:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你平常都是跟西圆寺一起吃的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.46,0:16:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是 我通常都是一个人吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.13,0:16:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.94,0:16:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.74,0:16:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？有这回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很奇怪对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.05,0:16:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.55,0:17:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在伦敦的公园 看到了好多的松鼠呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.42,0:17:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,松鼠？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.72,0:17:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊 那还是在城市里的公园喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.62,0:17:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想想真是稀奇 英国的松鼠感觉跟日本的鸽子好像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.20,0:17:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.60,0:17:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.03,0:17:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在日本根本不能想象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.13,0:17:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在普通的公园里会有松鼠这回事对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.10,0:17:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,松鼠也只能在宠物店看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕 已经这么晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.79,0:17:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.62,0:17:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有 松鼠从树上向我飞过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.59,0:17:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.23,0:17:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…真的是吓了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 我该…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.87,0:17:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.94,0:17:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,松鼠它…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.50,0:17:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.64,0:17:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,松鼠它…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我该回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.61,0:18:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你 请你听我说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.98,0:18:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你 请你…请你听我说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.59,0:18:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.65,0:18:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰 好慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.43,0:18:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.49,0:18:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对 葵大小姐现在在房间里 请稍等一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.54,0:18:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是薰吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.37,0:19:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在换她听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.14,0:19:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 对不起 事情变成这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.48,0:19:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊 那今晚你就要在朋友家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.72,0:19:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了 那晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.26,0:19:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰少爷他不回来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.96,0:19:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 今天好像要住在朋友家的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.73,0:19:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.73,0:19:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还不会睡 所以请葵大小姐去休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熬夜是皮肤粗糙的根源喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.81,0:19:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.48,0:19:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 糟糕 蒂娜她怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.09,0:19:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实她今天跟花菱学长的朋友起了点冲突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.12,0:19:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜你不要紧吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.23,0:19:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是…阿薰你搞什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她一直都是这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.87,0:20:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这…这到底是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.00,0:20:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有点事情啦 那今天晚上就先这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.44,0:20:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.87,0:20:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来 回到房间去吧 学姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.14,0:20:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过我还真的是吓了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.75,0:20:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女孩就突然对花菱学长吻了下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.75,0:20:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女孩？接吻？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.59,0:20:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰 这到底是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.90,0:20:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道薰今晚要住的地方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.65,0:20:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.12,0:21:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 晚安 小繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.23,0:21:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱少爷跟我一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.80,0:21:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小繭
